HEADWORD: Parqueted
<hw>Par"quet*ed</hw> <pr>(p⟦aum⟧r*k⟦amac⟧d")</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Formed in parquetry; inlaid with wood in small and differently
colored figures.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>One room <qex>parqueted</qex> with yew, which I liked well.</q>
<rj><qau>Evelyn.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

